item.description:
Be careful and do not bring signs that would cause a problem. This area will be packed with bused in union members many from out of our state. I'll be there.

Semper Fi,

Jerry
item.how_to_find_us: We will have the US Flag on a large flag pole
item.why: The public sector unions are organizing via radio and the net to bus in protesters to scare our NH State Representatives. This action is being done much like what happened in Wisconsin. We need to rally in support of our NH legislators.
item.name: Rally to Support Our NH State Legislators at the Capital
